{"tid":1815884,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Luke在蘋果登文寄語香港人","createTime":"2020-01-08T00:32:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T00:32:36.000Z","uid":294066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6df096bce886b4e0e505ec92e25a0c5c906ae8be","tid":1815884,"uid":294066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T00:32:36.000Z","msg":"一直實際行動支持香港的英國政客Luke，在蘋果登文寄語。給忙人的簡單中文重點：<br />\n1. 拉攏國際未夠力<br />\n2. 無大台雖好，但難以進行國際遊說。可試無實權的輪任發言人（我覺得民間記者會就是嘗試做這角色）<br />\n3. 國際要知道你們的要求。可以試想對國際社會的三大訴求，讓國際簽訂同意。<br />\n4. 別放棄國際遊說<br />\n5. 需顧大局，尤其勇武<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20200107/60460122\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200107%2F60460122&d=rLp99s1CaA%2FTm5LA4NL6TUuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=ba67f9f6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200107%2F60460122&h=111b7307\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20200107/60460122</a><br />\n<br />\n可以去佢twitter留言回應<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/lukedepulford/status/1214527945244598273?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flukedepulford%2Fstatus%2F1214527945244598273%3Fs%3D19&d=rLp99s1CaA%2FTm5LA4NL6TUuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=f5b0b641\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flukedepulford%2Fstatus%2F1214527945244598273%3Fs%3D19&h=182271fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/lukedepulford/status/1214527945244598273?s=19</a>"}]}